OL,3,CCouncil unveil plan to create 'Green
OL,4,CEnergy Hub' near Annan
OL,6,FPlans to turn the site of the former
OL,7,FChapelcross Nuclear Power station near
OL,8,FAnnan in Dumfries and Galloway into a
OL,9,FGreen Energy Hub were released by the
OL,10,Farea's council on Tuesday.
OL,12,FThe site, which opened in 1959,
OL,13,Foriginally produced weapons grade
OL,14,Fplutonium for the countries nuclear
OL,15,Fweapons programme. It also produced
OL,16,Fpower for the national grid before
OL,17,Fbeginning decommissioning in 2004.
