OL,3,CCouncil unveil plan to create 'Green
OL,4,CEnergy Hub' near Annan
OL,6,FDumfries and Galloway Council believe
OL,7,Fa Green Energy Hub on the site would
OL,8,Fprovide jobs in the local area and a
OL,9,Fboost for the economy. In a statement
OL,10,Fthe potential Hub was described as a
OL,11,F"multi-million pound, net-zero focused
OL,12,Fdevelopment."
OL,14,FIt would include hydrogen production,
OL,15,Fstorage and associated logistics,
OL,16,Fadvanced manufacturing, energy and
OL,17,Fenterprise campuses across 60 acres of
OL,18,Fthe 210 acre site.
