OL,3,CCouncil unveil plan to create 'Green
OL,4,CEnergy Hub' near Annan
OL,6,FIn a statement Council Leader Gail
OL,7,FMacgregor, said; "By commissioning
OL,8,Fthis masterplan, we have a clear
OL,9,Fvision for delivering future jobs
OL,10,Fwhich supports our transition to net
OL,11,Fzero for the region.
OL,13,F"We are united with Nuclear
OL,14,FDecommissioning Authority (NDA) and
OL,15,FSouth of Scotland Enterprise in our
OL,16,Fambition for the future of Chapelcross
OL,17,Fas a powerful force for change in the
OL,18,Flocal economy and look forward to the
OL,19,Fdesign developing.'"
