OL,6,FThe Council also believe such a
OL,7,Fdevelopment would aid the region in
OL,8,Fbecoming carbon neutral by 2040.
OL,10,FThe NDA are looking for a partner to
OL,11,Fdevelop plans for the site, which is
OL,12,Fbacked by significant funding from
OL,13,Fboth the UK and Scottish Governments.
